en_495957_0	By responding to a request made by the principal at Galle Sanghamitta College, 581 Brigade troops of the 58 Division and Sri Lanka Army Women’s Corps (SLAWC) gave their support to make the ‘Sangamith Spedizione 18’, a success on Saturday (29).
en_495957_1	Army troops provided their adventurous features before the final leg of the day’s event at the college premises.
en_495957_2	36 scout groups from island-wide schools and 26 Army personnel participated in the event.
